{"id": 1830, "genre": 1000, "title": "最近哪些时候你会感到自己的注意力被透支了？", "description": "你可能没意识到，你每天平均会接收 34GB 的互联网信息量，阅读近 10W 字的内容。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 12348, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170802225235hVqJUw8TXEOLZkI6.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-08T17:00:52Z", "questions": [{"id": 2717, "title": "最近哪些时候你会感到自己的注意力被透支了？", "content": "哪些时候你会感到自己的注意力被透支了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 226782, "content": "一边听播客或者音乐一边试图干正事，两边信息都没接收全", "image": "img/option/option/201708022342089MbhVNYlU6e0rDLx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226783, "content": "看微信文章的时候，先拉一下比较长就快速刷过去，只知道个大概", "image": "img/option/option/20170802234230df2nLkMlIiN6JeqX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226788, "content": "热点出现，总忍不住辗转三四个软件重复看一堆信息量没差的标题党报道", "image": "img/option/option/20170802232225RtJeZd2EnBq0F5Sk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226789, "content": "试图一边运动一边学习，一套动作下来光顾着喘，不知道听了啥", "image": "img/option/option/20170802233530UoTqCmB5PtgXbQdZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226790, "content": "找一个问题的满意答案，得看上好多自说自话的胡扯", "image": "img/option/option/20170802233615cS6E1Jvdp7bz2KC8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226792, "content": "朋友圈点开得太频繁，相同的状态会看到许多次", "image": "img/option/option/20170802233743eF9NVj7T63qHJO8m.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226794, "content": "隔三差五就有一个购物节，到处都是优惠信息，光是看规则就占了很多时间", "image": "img/option/option/20170802233913Y8OH0jJMitnRXI67.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 226795, "content": "app上的无用通知和促销短信，永远也退订不完", "image": "img/option/option/20170802233945qGmF3yoxzXQJ45T6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}